scenes.description: Anya Melfissa is evicted from her apartment for not paying rent.
Anya wanders the streets at night, lamenting the difficulties of being human before falling asleep on a bench.
Anya wakes up in a studio and is recruited by Mr. Yagoo to become a VTuber idol.

subtitles.original: Jangan- jangan nggak, kayak misalnya, saya bayar bulan depan gitu. Apakah boleh?
subtitles.english: Wait, no, like, for example, I can pay next month. Is that okay?

subtitles.original: Gak boleh dasar freeloader! Sudah berbulan-bulan kau belum bayar ya! Kalau masih gak bisa bayar juga hari ini, maka pergi sekarang juga dari sini!
subtitles.english: No way, you freeloader! You haven't paid for months! If you still can't pay today, then get out of here right now!

subtitles.original: Aaaaaaaaaaa! Bentar Ibu, bentar!
subtitles.english: AAAAAAAAAA! Wait, ma'am, wait!

subtitles.original: Ternyata jadi manusia susah juga ya.
subtitles.english: Being human is harder than I thought.

subtitles.original: Harus kerja dan melakukan beberapa hal lain hanya untuk bisa makan dan tinggal di tempat yang enak.
subtitles.english: You have to work and do many other things just to eat and live in a nice place.

subtitles.original: Mungkin menjadi manusia memang bukan ide yang bagus.
subtitles.english: Maybe becoming human wasn't such a good idea after all.

subtitles.original: Sangat susah beradaptasi.
subtitles.english: It's so hard to adapt.

subtitles.original: Padahal aku adalah senjata legendaris dari masa lalu.
subtitles.english: And yet, I'm a legendary weapon from the past.

subtitles.original: Kenapa aku harus melakukan semua hal merepotkan ini?
subtitles.english: Why do I have to do all these troublesome things?

subtitles.original: Hah... aku capek hari ini.
subtitles.english: *Sigh*... I'm tired today.

subtitles.original: Tidur di bangku di sini dulu deh.
subtitles.english: I'll just sleep on this bench for now.

subtitles.original: Good night.
subtitles.english: Good night.

subtitles.original: Halo. Akhirnya kamu terbangun.
subtitles.english: Hello. You're finally awake.

subtitles.original: Apa? Ini di mana? Anda siapa?
subtitles.english: What? Where is this? Who are you?

subtitles.original: Kamu pingsan di depan studio kami.
subtitles.english: You passed out in front of our studio.

subtitles.original: Kenalkan, nama saya Mr. Yagoo.
subtitles.english: Nice to meet you. I'm Mr. Yagoo.

subtitles.original: Silakan minum minuman hangat ini dulu.
subtitles.english: Please, have some of this warm drink.

subtitles.original: Mr. Yagoo...? Mr. Yagoo...?
subtitles.english: Mr. Yagoo...? Mr. Yagoo...?

subtitles.original: ちょっと怪しいんだけど…
subtitles.english: (Okay, this is VERY suspicious.)

subtitles.original: Ya sudahlah. Salam kenal juga.
subtitles.english: Whatever. Nice to meet you too.

subtitles.original: Mungkin tidak terlihat dari penampilan, tapi saya merupakan senjata kuno yang legendaris.
subtitles.english: I might not look like it, but I'm actually a legendary ancient weapon.

subtitles.original: Yah, walaupun baru diusir dari tempat kos saya.
subtitles.english: Well, although I was just kicked out of my boarding house.

subtitles.original: Makanya! Itu dia!
subtitles.english: That's why! Exactly!

subtitles.original: Kenapa sih manusia itu begitu kejam?
subtitles.english: Why are humans so cruel?

subtitles.original: Mana egois pula... saya sungguh tidak paham!
subtitles.english: And so selfish... I really don't understand!

subtitles.original: Anak muda zaman sekarang tuh begini semua ya?
subtitles.english: Is this how all young people are these days?

subtitles.original: Terdengar berat sekali.
subtitles.english: That sounds rough.

subtitles.original: Benar kan!
subtitles.english: Right?!

subtitles.original: Saya tidak tahu harus bagaimana sekarang.
subtitles.english: I really don't know what to do anymore.

subtitles.original: Bagaimana jika anda menjadi talent dari agensi kami?
subtitles.english: Well... how about becoming a talent for our agency?

subtitles.original: Menjadi seorang idol!
subtitles.english: As an idol!

subtitles.original: Eh? Apa maksudnya?
subtitles.english: Eh? What do you mean?

subtitles.original: Talent... maksudnya jadi idola VTuber?
subtitles.english: Talent... you mean like an idol VTuber?

subtitles.original: Eh? Seperti Tokino Sora, idola VTuber terkenal itu?
subtitles.english: Eh? Like Tokino Sora, that famous idol VTuber?

subtitles.original: Benar. Dia juga bagian dari kami, hololive production.
subtitles.english: That's right. She's also part of our hololive production.

subtitles.original: Sebagai gantinya, kamu bisa tinggal di sini sementara waktu.
subtitles.english: In exchange, you can stay here for the time being.

subtitles.original: Aku mau! Mau, mau!
subtitles.english: Count me in!

subtitles.original: この生活の 虜になっちゃうよ Lady
subtitles.english: I'll become a prisoner of this life, Lady.

subtitles.original: 光を失った おさがりの宝石を 永久に纏って
subtitles.english: Forever wearing second-hand jewels that have lost their light.

subtitles.original: トリコロージュ / Lyrics + Composition: 煮ル果実
subtitles.english: Tricologe / Lyrics + Composition: Nilfruits

subtitles.original: 救われたの光 救いが虚無になるなんて
subtitles.english: The light that saved me became a void,

subtitles.original: まるでフィクション トラパネーション 浮き足気分になってんだ
subtitles.english: Just like fiction, trepanation, I'm feeling restless.

subtitles.original: 足枷と鎖に縛られて たった一度の光で会うため
subtitles.english: Bound by shackles and chains, just to meet with that one-time light,

subtitles.original: この部屋でずっと待ってる 何かを待つ囚人
subtitles.english: Waiting in this room forever, a prisoner waiting for something.

subtitles.original: 出されたものは満遍なく 残さず平らげて
subtitles.english: Eating everything that was served without leaving anything behind,

subtitles.original: 異端な死よりも 誰よりも無個性だった
subtitles.english: Being more personality-less than anyone else, even more than a heretical death.

subtitles.original: 住めば都 暗い歌を何度も何度も吐き捨てて
subtitles.english: Any place is home, spitting out dark songs over and over again,

subtitles.original: 挙句の果て ふれる行為自体が苦手になった
subtitles.english: In the end, I became bad at the act of touching itself.

subtitles.original: 夜中 ふとに映った 煌めく仮面舞踏会
subtitles.english: In the middle of the night, a sparkling masquerade ball suddenly reflected.

subtitles.original: 馬鹿らしいほどに 狂おしいほどに 年甲斐もなく惹き込まれたら
subtitles.english: If I'm drawn in so ridiculously, so maddeningly, regardless of my age.

subtitles.original: この生活の 虜になっちゃうよ Lady
subtitles.english: I'll become a prisoner of this life, Lady.

subtitles.original: よく似合ってるってさ お誂え向きだってさ その後のことは見向きもしないくせに
subtitles.english: You say it suits me well, you say it's just right, even though you won't even look at what happens after.

subtitles.original: 生活の 虜になっちゃうよ Lady Lady
subtitles.english: A prisoner of life, Lady Lady.

subtitles.original: 痛みだってさ 言えぬ傷だってさ すべて生き抜いた証
subtitles.english: Even pain, even wounds that can't be spoken of, are all proof of having survived.

subtitles.original: 乗り越える試練 他愛もないことでしょう
subtitles.english: A trial to overcome, it's nothing significant, is it?

subtitles.original: 少し欠けてるピンコパール 迷子になったアイオライト
subtitles.english: A slightly chipped pink opal, a lost iolite,

subtitles.original: 埃を被るトパーズ 孤独なアメトリンもみんな
subtitles.english: A dusty topaz, and lonely ametrine, everyone.

subtitles.original: それぞれ着飾って 濁って重くなって
subtitles.english: Dressing up in their own ways, getting muddy and heavy,

subtitles.original: 奈落の底 牢獄に 沈んでいくとしても
subtitles.english: Even if they sink into the bottom of the abyss, into a prison.

subtitles.original: 訪れた幸せかぼちゃ 祝祭日みたいに
subtitles.english: Like the happiness that arrived, like a public holiday,

subtitles.original: すでに決められた予定調和
subtitles.english: A pre-established harmony that's already been decided.
